<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>Sound—Type Preview</title>
<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#0b0b0d;
    --panel:#121216;
    --panel-2:#18181d;
    --border:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    --text:rgba(255,255,255,.94);
    --muted:rgba(255,255,255,.62);
  }

  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  html,body{height:100%;margin:0}
  body{
    font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255,255,255,.06), transparent 28%),
      radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(255,255,255,.04), transparent 24%),
      var(--bg);
    color:var(--text);
  }

  .layout{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: 320px 1fr;
    gap:20px;
    height:100vh;
    padding:20px;
  }

  .sidebar{
    background:rgba(18,18,22,.86);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:18px;
    padding:18px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  }

  .eyebrow{
    font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:.16em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--muted);
    margin-bottom:10px;
  }

  h1{
    font-size:24px;
    line-height:1.05;
    margin:0 0 12px;
  }

  p{
    margin:0 0 14px;
    color:var(--muted);
    line-height:1.55;
    font-size:14px;
  }

  .card{
    margin-top:16px;
    padding:14px;
    border-radius:14px;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .card strong{
    display:block;
    font-size:12px;
    letter-spacing:.08em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    margin-bottom:8px;
  }

  .steps{
    display:grid;
    gap:8px;
    padding:0;
    margin:0;
    list-style:none;
  }

  .steps li{
    padding:10px 12px;
    border-radius:10px;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.025);
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);
    font-size:13px;
  }

  .preview-shell{
    min-width:0;
    background:rgba(10,10,12,.82);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:22px;
    padding:14px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
  }

  .preview-topbar{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:space-between;
    gap:12px;
    padding:6px 6px 14px;
  }

  .dots{
    display:flex;
    gap:8px;
  }

  .dot{
    width:10px;
    height:10px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.16);
  }

  .urlbar{
    flex:1;
    min-width:0;
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    background:var(--panel);
    color:var(--muted);
    border-radius:999px;
    padding:10px 14px;
    font-size:13px;
    white-space:nowrap;
    overflow:hidden;
    text-overflow:ellipsis;
  }

  iframe{
    width:100%;
    height:calc(100vh - 88px);
    border:none;
    border-radius:16px;
    background:#000;
    display:block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px){
    .layout{
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      height:auto;
      min-height:100vh;
    }

    iframe{
      height:78vh;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="layout">
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="eyebrow">Local Preview</div>
      <h1>Sound—Type UI</h1>
      <p>Tenhle wrapper ti otevře finální HTML jako čistý preview frame, takže můžeš rychle zkontrolovat layout, panel a celkový dojem bez dalšího nastavování.</p>

      <div class="card">
        <strong>Jak použít</strong>
        <ul class="steps">
          <li>Ulož tenhle soubor jako <code>preview.html</code>.</li>
          <li>Ulož finální app jako <code>soundtype-ui-polished.html</code>.</li>
          <li>Pokud má jiný název, uprav atribut <code>src</code> níže.</li>
          <li>Pak otevři <code>preview.html</code> v prohlížeči.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="preview-shell">
      <div class="preview-topbar">
        <div class="dots">
          <span class="dot"></span>
          <span class="dot"></span>
          <span class="dot"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="urlbar">./soundtype-ui-polished.html</div>
      </div>

      <iframe
        title="Sound-Type Preview"
        src="soundtype-ui-polished.html">
      </iframe>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
